             *** Prospectus for the Convertible Bond ***

At 1PM on Friday 11/4/94, the convertible bond pays either $10 or
the firm's earnings divided by 760, whichever is less.  In addition,
the bond may be converted into one share of stock.

The firm's earnings are $10,000 times the sum of the absolute
percentage changes in the DJIA from Monday 10/31 (vs the previous
day), through Friday 11/4/94.

You may place up to 10 orders in the convertible bond market. 
